  <entry>
    <title>Hexo</title>
    <link href="/2021/02/19/hexo/"/>
    <url>/2021/02/19/hexo/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Steps-on-using-Hexo-to-build-a-blog"><a href="#Steps-on-using-Hexo-to-build-a-blog" class="headerlink" title="Steps on using Hexo to build a blog"></a>Steps on using Hexo to build a blog</h1><h2 id="1-Install-nodejs"><a href="#1-Install-nodejs" class="headerlink" title="1. Install nodejs"></a>1. Install nodejs</h2><figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmake">sudo apt <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span> nodejs<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-npm-change-source"><a href="#2-npm-change-source" class="headerlink" title="2. npm change source"></a>2. npm change source</h2><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">sudo npm install -g cnpm --registry=https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>registry.npm.taobao.org <span class="hljs-comment"># taobao source </span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-Install-hexo-from-cnpm-source"><a href="#3-Install-hexo-from-cnpm-source" class="headerlink" title="3. Install hexo from cnpm source"></a>3. Install hexo from cnpm source</h2><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs avrasm">sudo cnpm install -g hexo-<span class="hljs-keyword">cli</span><br>hexo -v <span class="hljs-meta"># check whether installed</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-Initialize-hexo-directory"><a href="#4-Initialize-hexo-directory" class="headerlink" title="4. Initialize hexo directory"></a>4. Initialize hexo directory</h2><figure class="highlight dos"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dos"><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> hexo-blog &amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> hexo-blog<br>sudo hexo init<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="5-Some-hexo-commands"><a href="#5-Some-hexo-commands" class="headerlink" title="5. Some hexo commands"></a>5. Some hexo commands</h2><figure class="highlight verilog"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs verilog">hexo s # start hexo service locally<br>hexo clean # clean files<br>hexo g # <span class="hljs-keyword">generate</span> hexo files, <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="6-hexo-cheatsheet"><a href="#6-hexo-cheatsheet" class="headerlink" title="6. hexo cheatsheet"></a>6. hexo cheatsheet</h2><p>hexo posts add photos</p><p>src: <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/m0_47415152/article/details/108606956?utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-baidujs_title-2&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.4242">https://blog.csdn.net/m0_47415152/article/details/108606956?utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-baidujs_title-2&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.4242</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
